snippet.title: Kill To Collect - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Prior to the new Titan Quest expansions and the upcoming Alone in the Dark remake, Pieces Interactive tried their hand at a cyberpunk themed hack & slash rougelike in 2016.

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/241760/Kill_to_Collect/
